    "DiscussionIn this case study we aimed to assess whether GPT-4 could be used to automatically construct two health economic analyses based on descriptions of the model's assumptions, methods should be distinguished from model conceptualisation, estimation of parameter values and model validation (technical and external) that were not automated during this study.",
